Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.11,0:02:28.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}渐次斑驳  世界之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:34.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕らは終りへ旅をする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:34.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}身在旅途　至终焉之河
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:40.74,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その束の間に　君と出会った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:40.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}刹那之间  逢见君影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:44.61,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}命を削るように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:44.61,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如日削月割
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:56.63,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}時の向こうに確かにあった　遥かな故郷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:56.63,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}故乡迢迢  时之彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:59.69,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君とゆけるの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:59.69,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}与君共往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:02.74,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛も見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:02.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无爱无心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:14.43,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜の向こうに　幻の空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:14.43,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜之彼方  如幻苍空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:20.83,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:24.99,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}错综
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你带路  跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要放我走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管那么多  今天的事就忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也别再牵扯进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次估计救不了你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的存在  非常碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底做错了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自放走可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是喜欢超自然现象的神堕人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为无视掉没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就这样放任接近秘密的人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这样就对神堕人出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不正是违背了戒律吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒律吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来那个女孩是猎户大人的同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前摘花五十铃差点堕落的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为猎户大人稍有些公私不分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想有无谓的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:04:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于落神之式能请交给担任猎户的我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  请恕我冒昧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今后请勿独断行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这样的问题只不过是小事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天我委托了「专家」  去把强劲的「蜜」排除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排除？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是你的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田家的当家  重三大人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我们亲手抓住「蜜」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让「专家」来解决
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不直接下手的话也不算违背戒律吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来交给「专家」的名单上也有猎户大人的同学的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘花？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘花五十铃也缺席吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝雾要也难得请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在打算去地方资料馆调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要管好自己的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题的话要马上去「中心」…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的身体只有自己最清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些话想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛西大人  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎户大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引起骚动就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视这个小鬼  直接去「蜜」那边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己做的兔耳青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢兔耳青蛙先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的话送给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您的联络
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神人的病症的真正治疗法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其实现就是你的理想对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  在犹豫什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以相信你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说是神人的病症
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严格来说不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神人和人类是不同的种类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同的种类  不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说  是人非人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本和普通人类没有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除去那个被诅咒的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿命？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在有些场合下会抑制不住冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了扭转这可悲的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此希望能和你的公司一同开发疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤木先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:10:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须…一定要完成这个研究
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此请你助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  虽然我不该这么说  但能否请你保证
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份资料上记载的神人的事情只有你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…为什么跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开这里  赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你跟我们来一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎户大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同学  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎户大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当家的命令  请让开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经忠告过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再违背当家的命令的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的地位真的会岌岌可危
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样值得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就先退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别多说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  院长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  这种时候来访
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…今天是作为栉名田家的人来此的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白狼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白狼大人终于要去神域了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真那小姐  不  白狼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经有心理准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万事俱备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一步…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只差一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三重子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…  难不成！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙  又要从我这里掠夺了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎户大人  请问您这是何意？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天您帮助朝雾要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这回您又妨碍我们捉拿九澄博士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此  遵照猎户的守则
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将追究您应负的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠  葛西所言当真？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵照规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除你猎户的身份  并禁止你出门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不舒服了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯…  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  明天我们一起去探望香织姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西  是什么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是今天  一位很可爱的大姐姐给的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像穿的是跟哥哥一样的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:14:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是发生过什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  是的  我是九澄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚了还麻烦你  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  好的  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织姐  去哪儿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是搬家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都一声不吭的  说走就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚大哥也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能先回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也可以  可为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.06,0:16:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个地方想去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.57,0:16:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到  你竟会主动联系我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.11,0:16:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你想说的  又是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后  我又想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我周围  有被贤木先生你称为怪物的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话  我很怕他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上  我也有过被他们袭击过的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得  应该是事出有因的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  应该是有非这么做不可的理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  那个手执巨镰的少女…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的同班同学栉名田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在这之前  曾经救了我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救你一命？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我几乎可以说是一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想搞个明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那些家伙里面  有良心的人  也许还是有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那样  要是我有证据的话呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我有他们是极度危险的怪物的证据呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回我就让你好好看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是真相
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  还是那个强效的蜜的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们委托的「专家」来电话说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经成功地将那「蜜」——九澄博士给抓到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监禁地点仍旧是以前的那处工地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是优秀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  处置的事  就交给那「专家」来干对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  听他说  之后就按照家主大人的意思  随时执行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么  那就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田眠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄君在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这只怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实交代  九澄君在那儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费我好大功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  我不会马上杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想死得这么容易
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于你  对于杀了三重子的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会给予和我悲痛相当的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我是九澄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  贤木先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  现在就出来么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  你不是想知道么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你要给我看什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  先到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤木先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤木先生  开门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤木先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.47,0:21:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:21:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄…  君…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁大眼睛好好看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.08,0:22:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你想知道的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.59,0:22:18.17,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れないで　この想いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.59,0:22:18.17,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}勿忘怀  此相思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.21,0:22:28.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ボクらが信じた　愛ノ共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.21,0:22:28.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(425,440)\fad(100,100)\fs18}うた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.21,0:22:28.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}吾等深信  爱之共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:38.10,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}抱き締めた夜には　欠けた月が啼く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:38.10,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}拥夜入眠  残月鸣泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.02,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}繰り返す罪には　躊躇いの月が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.02,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(363,440)\fad(100,100)\fs18}とまど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.02,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}罪劫轮回  惑月迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:50.18,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}満ちる　溶ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:50.18,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}满盈圆缺  无痕冰消
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:56.78,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いくつもの心が　キミを縛るなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:56.78,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}千千心结  若缚君影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:23:03.17,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}墜ちてゆく決意が許されるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:23:03.17,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}则至神允  坠天之志
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.54,0:23:07.40,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛なの、と　信じたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.54,0:23:07.40,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}深信此爱  永不相弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:14.73,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}微かな声　手繰りよせて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:14.73,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}细语声中忆往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.77,0:23:20.53,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}交錯わる　闇の調べ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.77,0:23:20.53,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱恨交结暗之乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:27.30,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}繋いでゆく　この想いは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:27.30,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}此相思  永相连
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:38.00,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ボクらが夢見た　刻ノ謳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:38.00,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}入我梦  时之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九吻所为何？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.16,0:23:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难逆心之火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.97,0:23:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未尝禁果味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.21,0:23:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因抑心魔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.58,0:23:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刑法可乎悲？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.35,0:23:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其人当为我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.10,0:24:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来  我究竟都在看着什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟都在相信着什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.36,0:24:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.27,0:24:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若还不能凭着自己的一双手臂  以及一双眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.63,0:24:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将真相看个一清二楚的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.93,0:24:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  密室
